---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Chyron App">
  <main class="container mx-auto p-4">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center my-8 animate__animated animate__fadeIn">Chyron App</h1>
    <div class="card bg-base-200 shadow-xl">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h2 class="card-title">Web-based Chyron Display</h2>
        <p>Create and display customizable graphical overlays for live streaming and recording.</p>
        <div class="card-actions justify-end">
          <a href="/chyron" class="btn btn-primary">Open Chyron</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Features</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
        <li>Customizable text and icons for streaming overlays</li>
        <li>Real-time editing with content editable fields</li>
        <li>Smooth animations and transitions</li>
        <li>Local storage persistence</li>
        <li>Compatible with OBS Studio</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    
    <div class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">OBS Integration</h2>
      <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2">
        <li>In OBS Studio, add a new "Browser" source</li>
        <li>Set the URL to the Chyron page (e.g., http://localhost:4321/chyron)</li>
        <li>Set an appropriate width and height (e.g., 1920x200)</li>
        <li>Enable "Control audio via OBS" to prevent audio issues</li>
        <li>Click "OK" to add the source</li>
      </ol>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>